OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy in places to start on
OL,6,FSaturday, perhaps brighter for north
OL,7,FTayside, some brightness developing
OL,8,Ffor most areas but some outbreaks of
OL,9,Flight rain too, wintry on higher
OL,10,Fground in the west.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FClear spells developing
OL,13,Fduring the evening, but clouding over
OL,14,Flater in the night with freshening
OL,15,Fsouthwesterly winds and some outbreaks
OL,16,Fof rain through the night.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
