OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FFresh southwesterly winds and
OL,6,Foutbreaks of rain through the day, a
OL,7,Ffew drier spells developing for Fife
OL,8,Fbut further rain by evening, feeling
OL,9,Fmild around east Fife.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FCloudy
OL,12,Fwith outbreaks of rain through Sunday
OL,13,Fand Monday with winds strengthening,
OL,14,Fbut still some good dry and bright or
OL,15,Fsunny spells. A mostly dry day Tuesday
OL,16,Fwith sunny spells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
